                  </persName>
             for the residuary legatee and executor instead of Mr. Slack, who was the sole executor and residuary legatee, that was the main object of the will; it was determined to get at this will, how it was I cannot tell you, nor can Underwood, but by the relation of 
               <persName id="t17860111-2-person184">
                  Nathaniel
                   Goodridge
               <interp inst="t17860111-2-person184" type="surname" value="Goodridge"></interp>
