                     <interp inst="t17860111-2-person186" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , who was a publican at the Cooper's Arms on Saffron-hill, and the brother of 
               <persName id="t17860111-2-person187">
                  Nathaniel
                   Goodridge
               <interp inst="t17860111-2-person187" type="surname" value="Goodridge"></interp>
